                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<p>This archive displays all pages that have been featured on the site's front page in commemoration of special event days or monthly themes. These pages have been selected for thematic reasons, in addition to being well-received by the site community overall.</p>
<p>The forum thread announcing these features is <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-1112343/holiday-featured-pages">here</a>.</p>
<hr />
<p>Staff Note: As of 2019, the Event Featured front page block has been replaced with the <a href="/reviewers-spotlight-archive">Reviewers' Spotlight</a>!</p>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2018&nbsp;EVENT&nbsp;FEATURES&nbsp;JANUARY&nbsp;-&nbsp;APRIL</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2018&nbsp;EVENT&nbsp;FEATURES&nbsp;JANUARY&nbsp;-&nbsp;APRIL</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<h4 id="toc0"><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">January 2018:</span> <em>reanimation</em> tag month</span></h4>
<p><strong>1 January 2018 - <em>reanimation</em> tag month featured page #1</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-2838">SCP-2838</a> (Stellar Reincarnation Column) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=560062&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="minmin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=560062)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;">minmin</a></span></li>
<li><em>Aerial exploration of SCP-2838 reveals that each luminescent object, hereby designated SCP-2838-1, is a mass of plasma roughly the size and shape of a human being&#8230;</em></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>11 January 2018 - <em>reanimation</em> tag month featured page #2</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-1818">SCP-1818</a> (Flying Rabbits) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bunton" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1225550); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1225550&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="Bunton" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1225550)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bunton" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1225550); return false;">Bunton</a></span></li>
<li><em>The effects of this event are known to begin to manifest inside the plane itself, roughly ten to twenty (10-20) minutes into the flight.</em></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>21 January 2018 - <em>reanimation</em> tag month featured page #3</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-1405">SCP-1405</a> (A Large Prehistoric Sloth) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kenji-and-co" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1612384); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1612384&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="Kenji_and_co" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1612384)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kenji-and-co" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1612384); return false;">Kenji_and_co</a></span></li>
<li><em>In its inactive (or camouflage) state, SCP-1405 appears to be a normal model: X-ray scans indicate it is composed primarily of plastic resin on an internal metal scaffolding.</em></li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc1"><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">February 2018:</span> <em>engraved</em> tag month</span></h4>
<p><strong>1 February 2018 - <em>engraved</em> tag month featured page #1</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-2762">SCP-2762</a> (Moon Snakes) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/anaxagoras" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1019930); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1019930&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="Anaxagoras" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1019930)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/anaxagoras" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1019930); return false;">Anaxagoras</a></span></li>
<li><em>Every full moon at solar midnight for the target of SCP-2762, a 2762 Activation Event occurs. At this time, SCP-2762 begins to vibrate, and a green luminescence appears on the surface.</em></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>11 February 2018 - <em>engraved</em> tag month featured page #2</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-1184">SCP-1184</a> (Truth) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dragonnyxx" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(409420); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=409420&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="dragonnyxx" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=409420)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dragonnyxx" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(409420); return false;">dragonnyxx</a></span></li>
<li><em>Attempts to utilize SCP-1184 for its beneficial effects have been hampered by the fact that it also affects the speaker, who will become equally convinced of the truth of their statements.</em></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>21 February 2018 - <em>engraved</em> tag month featured page #3</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-1418">SCP-1418</a> (The Dowager's Comb) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sregan" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1386518); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1386518&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="SRegan" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1386518)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sregan" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1386518); return false;">SRegan</a></span></li>
<li><em>Its anomalous properties become apparent when worn by a human subject; the subject is rapidly transformed&#8230;</em></li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc2"><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">March 2018:</span> <em>satellite</em> tag month</span></h4>
<p><strong>1 March 2018 - <em>satellite</em> tag month featured page #1</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-1778">SCP-1778</a> (Valor) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-reach" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1779895); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1779895&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="Dr Reach" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1779895)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-reach" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1779895); return false;">Dr Reach</a></span></li>
<li><em>SCP-1778 is, to date, the only known spaceship of the Soyuz 7K-L2 series, designed by [REDACTED] and placed in orbit in 1966&#8230;</em></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>11 March 2018 - <em>satellite</em> tag month featured page #2</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-364">SCP-364</a> (Ionian Drop Point) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/quikngruvn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(333389); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=333389&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="Quikngruvn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=333389)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/quikngruvn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(333389); return false;">Quikngruvn</a></span></li>
<li><em>SCP-364 is a point several hundred meters above the volcano Surt on Io, the innermost of Jupiter’s Galilean satellites.</em></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>21 March 2018 - <em>satellite</em> tag month featured page #3</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-2146">SCP-2146</a> (The Space Whale) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/megalomaniacinchworm" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2193087); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2193087&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="MegalomaniacInchworm" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2193087)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/megalomaniacinchworm" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2193087); return false;">MegalomaniacInchworm</a></span></li>
<li><em>Once every Synodic Lunar month (29.5 days), SCP-2146 begins broadcasting radio signals, presently designated SCP-2146-1.</em></li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc3"><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">April 2018:</span> <em>currency</em> tag month</span></h4>
<p><strong>1 April 2018 - <em>currency</em> tag month featured page #1</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-2190">SCP-2190</a> (Phone calls from Mom) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1553042); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1553042&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="PeppersGhost" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1553042)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1553042); return false;">PeppersGhost</a></span></li>
<li><em>Additionally, individuals employed at financial institutions will immediately forget any instructions to alter or deny transactions from POI-2190-1's bank account.</em></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>11 April 2018 - <em>currency</em> tag month featured page #2</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-2855">SCP-2855</a> (Mr. Money) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2038009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="TyGently" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2038009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;">TyGently</a></span></li>
<li><em>SCP-2855 is anomalously affected by business transactions made regarding its ownership.</em></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>21 April 2018 - <em>currency</em> tag month featured page #3</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-1442">SCP-1442</a> (Incorporated) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meserach" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1507289); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1507289&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="Meserach" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1507289)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meserach" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1507289); return false;">Meserach</a></span></li>
<li><em>SCP-1442 is a corporation (known to shareholders, employees and the general public as &quot;████ ███████, Inc.&quot;) which anomalously produces signals coded into stock trades…</em></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>~</p>
