<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<h4 id="toc4"><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">May 2018:</span> <em>wooden</em> tag month</span></h4>
<p><strong>1 May 2018 - <em>wooden</em> tag month featured page #1</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-805">SCP-805</a> (Poison Wood Foal) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aura-vesta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(303015); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=303015&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="Aura Vesta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=303015)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aura-vesta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(303015); return false;">Aura Vesta</a></span></li>
<li><em>It is drawn toward human presences, actively seeking contact with skin, and has been reported as being 'very friendly' when approached.</em></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>11 May 2018 - <em>wooden</em> tag month featured page #2</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-3197">SCP-3197</a> (A Trickster God for the Modern Age) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zoltanberrigomo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3290527); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3290527&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="ZoltanBerrigomo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3290527)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zoltanberrigomo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3290527); return false;">ZoltanBerrigomo</a></span></li>
<li><em>Lead us not into overleverage / But deliver us from margin calls / For yours is the market and the profit and the glory</em></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>21 May 2018 - <em>wooden</em> tag month featured page #3</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-421">SCP-421</a> (Shoal of Driftwood) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirava" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(646034); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=646034&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="Sirava" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=646034)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirava" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(646034); return false;">Sirava</a></span></li>
<li><em>SCP-421 should be 'fed' on a bimonthly basis; standard feed consists of a wooden fishing vessel, typically at least 15 metres in length and preferably in a dilapidated condition.</em></li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc5"><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">June 2018:</span> <em>location</em> tag month</span></h4>
<p><strong>1 June 2018 - <em>location</em> tag month featured page #1</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-2191">SCP-2191</a> (“Dracula Factory”) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/metaphysician" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1698079); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1698079&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="Metaphysician" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1698079)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/metaphysician" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1698079); return false;">Metaphysician</a></span></li>
<li><em>The caverns of SCP-2191 are not thought to have formed naturally and were likely constructed ca. 4800 to 3000 BC.</em></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>11 June 2018 - <em>location</em> tag month featured page #2</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-257">SCP-257</a> (Professor William Woodsworth’s Collection of Curiosities) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tom-serveaux" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1274861); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1274861&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="Tom Serveaux" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1274861)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tom-serveaux" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1274861); return false;">Tom Serveaux</a></span></li>
<li><em>At irregular intervals, animals will appear within the zoo’s confines through an unknown manner.</em></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>21 June 2018 - <em>location</em> tag month featured page #3</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-2548">SCP-2548</a> (The Friendly Vacuum) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2038009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="TyGently" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2038009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;">TyGently</a></span></li>
<li><em>No mass of note, excluding cosmic dust particles, has been detected within SCP-2548 through visual observation or gravitational analysis.</em></li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc6"><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">July 2018:</span> <em>fire</em> tag month</span></h4>
<p><strong>1 July 2018 - <em>fire</em> tag month featured page #1</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-1045">SCP-1045</a> (Candle of Life) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drewbear" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(301632); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=301632&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="Drewbear" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=301632)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drewbear" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(301632); return false;">Drewbear</a></span></li>
<li><em>Testing has revealed that burning scented candles produces shadows of different figures.</em></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>11 July 2018 - <em>fire</em> tag month featured page #2</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-3885">SCP-3885</a> (The High-Octane Full-Throttle Adventures of the Exploding Zombie Gearheads) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3187823); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3187823&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="CadaverCommander" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3187823)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3187823); return false;">CadaverCommander</a></span></li>
<li><em>SCP-3885-01 were observed to periodically drive to surrounding townships, whereupon they would locate and steal vehicles from garages…</em></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>21 July 2018 - <em>fire</em> tag month featured page #3</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-1660">SCP-1660</a> (Unearthly Forest) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adam-henderson" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1350867); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1350867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869450" alt="Adam Henderson" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1350867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adam-henderson" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1350867); return false;">Adam Henderson</a></span></li>
